Ford Motor Credit Co unit Ford Motor Co raise 250 mln dlrs via offering note due 1990 yield 6.95 pct lead underwriter Goldman Sachs. The note 6-7/8 pct coupon price 99.80 yield 47 basis point comparable Treasury securities. Non-callable issue rat A-1 Moody's AA Standard Poor's. On October 7 1986 credit unit sell 200 mln dlrs same-maturity note rat A-1/A price yield 7.172 pct 77 basis point Treasuries. Reuter 